settings.lp-banner-alt-h: The Ideal Dog Food Created In Memory Of Two Best Friends
settings.lp-banner-alt-p: In commemoration of two best friends, Oscar & Milo's high quality, high protein and grain-free dog food recipes provide an ideal diet for your best friend, no matter the breed.

settings.title: More than just your average dog food.
settings.text: Every Oscar & Milo dog food recipe has been tailored to deliver high quality nutrition for your dog's requirements. No matter the breed, age or dietary requirements, there's an Oscar & Milo recipe that's right for your dog.

settings.lp-collection: All Oscar & Milo dog food recipes are expertly formulated to provide a complete high-protein, grain-free, delicious diet which your dog will keep coming back for.

settings.lp-i-p1-text: A complete meal in every recipe, with high meat content to help provide your dog with a naturally nutritious diet.
settings.lp-i-p2-text: All Oscar & Milo dog food recipes are completely grain-free, meaning no wheat, gluten, rice or grains across our range.
settings.lp-i-p3-text: Oscar & Milo believe in superior nutrition. If we wouldn't feed it to our furry friends, we won't feed it to yours.

settings.lp-banner-h: High Quality Super Premium Dog Food
settings.lp-banner-p: Quality, natural nutrition is at the heart of Oscar & Milo dog food, helping your dog live their life to the full.
